{"tid":2305501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會：周三起，暫時關閉所有場外投注處，直至另行通知。","createTime":"2020-11-29T16:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T18:32:05.000Z","uid":80564,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e44963ee3737712804738496d76764dc011f938e","tid":2305501,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"馬會表示，因應新型冠狀病毒疫情的最新發展，經詳細考慮有關情況後，決定由周三起，暫時關閉所有場外投注處，直至另行通知。<br />\n馬會指，顧客可於周一及二前往場外投注處開設或重啟投注戶口、進行投注戶口存款、兌換現金券或中獎彩票、辦理轉帳設定及進行其他顧客服務。於場外投注處暫時關閉期間，顧客可繼續使用電話投注熱線及馬會的流動應用程式等投注，並可透過應用程式利用轉數快、繳費靈及網上銀行的銀行繳付賬單服務等來存款<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬會所有場外投注處周三起暫時關閉<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414748&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414748%26refer%3DShare&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=894e5546\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414748%26refer%3DShare&h=4ea9bcee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414748&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"b66367f5fea1beee8b7ad8349ece23a4de582978","tid":2305501,"uid":184787,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"廢老末日"},{"pid":"f41c4ba32c08ffd0acef5e2f2d54d3a1a506af8c","tid":2305501,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a7c7b124d4520cdc279c88dfa21664d93eb96","tid":2305501,"uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b66367f5fea1beee8b7ad8349ece23a4de582978","tid":2305501,"uid":184787,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"廢老末日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"世界未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.g